text: allahda, ohuge dutayada yamkisi karanavak gæna niyoga kirimen anaturuva, ema karanavehi (eyata venas andamin venat) abhiprayan dærimata visvasin vana kisima pirimiyekuta ho gæhæniyakata ho ayitiyak næta. (ehi) allahtada, ohuge dutayatada kavurun ho venaskamak kalahot niyata vasayenma ovun prakata dur margayehima sitinnaha
